Aim_pe_aurora-beta11
by [pE]-YESS 9:56 AM Tuesday, March 25, 2158

** BEGIN TRANSMISSION*

    The Aurora, a distant outpost on Planet Eleethal, originally designed as a training ground for the military, is now just a series of abandoned buildings surrounded by junk.    In recent years it has been the center of many skirmishes between Terrorist and Counter-Terrorism groups.    There are Scout Sniper rifles on the roof of all 4 buildings, Colt M4A1 inside the blue base, and AK47 inside the red base.    Inbetween the red and blue bases are a series of other weapon drops including M3 shotgun, sg552 assault rifle, MP5 Navy, TMP, mac10 and Famas.

** END TRANSMISSION **

This is the 11th beta, but the first one I have posted on FPSBanana.   If you have any suggestions please feel free to comment.
